# Unity 项目 Git 忽略规则
# 过滤 Unity 生成/缓存/本地环境文件，避免提交到版本库

# --- Unity 缓存与构建输出 ---
[Ll]ibrary/
[Ll]ibrary/[Pp]ackageCache/
[Tt]emp/
[Oo]bj/
[Bb]uild/
[Bb]uilds/
[Ll]ogs/
[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/
[Mm]emoryCaptures/
[Rr]ecordings/
[Ee]xportedObj/
[Ss]erverData/
[Aa]ssets/AssetStoreTools*
[Aa]ssets/_Recovery/

# UPM 本地嵌入包（保留 manifest.json / packages-lock.json）
[Pp]ackages/*/
![Pp]ackages/manifest.json
![Pp]ackages/packages-lock.json

# --- IDE / 编辑器 ---
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.DotSettings.user
.consulo/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# --- Unity 自动生成的工程文件（由 Editor 重新生成）---
*.csproj
*.unityproj
*.sln
*.slnx
*.suo
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb
*.mdb
*.opendb
*.VC.db
*.pidb.meta
*.pdb.meta
*.mdb.meta

# --- 系统与杂项 ---
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
sysinfo.txt

# --- 构建产物与包 ---
*.apk
*.aab
*.unitypackage
*.app
*.ipa
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
init.gradle/
.gradle/
local.properties

# --- 崩溃与诊断 ---
[Cc]rashReport/
crashlytics-build.properties
*.stackdump

# --- 其他常见临时文件 ---
*.tmp
*.temp
*.log
*.bak
*.swp
*~
